<p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第一章&nbsp; 总则</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第一条&nbsp;&nbsp;为规范招生工作，维护广大考生的合法权益，保证招生工作的顺利进行，根据《中华人民共和国教育法》、《中华人民共和国高等教育法》及教育部普通高等学校招生工作的有关规定，并结合我校招生工作的具体情况，特制定本章程。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二条&nbsp;&nbsp;本章程适用于江西软件职业技术大学2023年普通本科、专科层次的招生工作。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三条&nbsp;&nbsp;依照教育部普通高等学校招生工作规定，学校招生工作遵循“公平竞争、公正选拔、公开程序，德智体美劳全面考核、综合评价、择优录取”的原则。　　</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二章&nbsp; 学校概况</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第四条&nbsp;&nbsp;学校全称：江西软件职业技术大学</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第五条&nbsp;&nbsp;国标代码：13776</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第六条&nbsp;&nbsp;办学层次及类型：民办本科层次职业高等学校</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第七条&nbsp;&nbsp;办学定位：学校秉承“创业创新、知识管理”的校训，实施“校企融合、产学互动”的办学模式，致力于培养全日制本、专科信息产业技术、技能人才。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第八条&nbsp;&nbsp;办学地点：江西省南昌市湾里区罗亭镇罗亭大道89号</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三章&nbsp; 组织机构</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第九条&nbsp;&nbsp;学校设有招生工作顾问委员会、招生工作领导小组、招生工作监督委员会，主要负责审议学校招生政策，对招生工作提供咨询意见，并对招生工作全程监督检查。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十条&nbsp;&nbsp;学校设有招生管理工作委员会，全面负责学校普通类招生工作；学校招生办公室是学校组织和实施普通类招生工作的常设机构，其主要职责是：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（一）执行国家、教育部有关招生法规、政策以及相关省（市、自治区）招生主管部门有关招生政策。执行学校招生章程及学校招生工作委员会的决定。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（二）根据学校年度招生计划，科学、合理地编制和实施分省分专业招生计划。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（三）组织开展学校招生宣传工作，与各职能部门、二级学院共同做好招生信息服务及咨询工作。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（四）负责学校录取各类考生，并负责处理录取中的各种问题。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（五）根据国家有关规定对录取新生进行入学资格复查。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十一条&nbsp;&nbsp;为加强对招生工作人员的纪律教育和责任约束，学校纪检监察室负责监督招生工作各项政策和规定的落实，切实维护广大考生和学校的合法权益。</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第四章&nbsp; 招生计划</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十二条&nbsp;&nbsp;根据江西省教育厅有关工作要求，学校综合考虑各省（自治区、直辖市）考生人数、生源质量、毕业生就业情况等因素，并结合历年招生实际情况，确定分省分专业计划。经教育部审核后由各省（自治区、直辖市）招生主管部门向社会公布。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十三条&nbsp;&nbsp;江西软件职业技术大学2023年招生类别分为普通类、艺术类和体育类，各类别招生人数和类别（批次）以各省（市、自治区）招生主管部门公布为准，或查阅我校对外公布的招生简章。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十四条&nbsp;&nbsp;学校实行专业招生计划动态平衡机制。对于社会需求量大且生源好的专业，可适当增加招生计划；对基础学科或就业形势好但报考人数少的专业，可采取一定措施予以扶持；对个别社会需求量小、学生报考少的专业，学校可调整其招生计划，对其采取减招、隔年招生或停招的办法。</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89); caret-color: red;">第五章&nbsp; 招生专业</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十五条&nbsp;&nbsp;本科招生专业（见学校招生网站（招生网 (jxuspt.com)）、官方公众号（江西软件职业技术大学招就处）公示信息，各省招生专业具体按照各省计划专刊公布专业执行）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十六条&nbsp;&nbsp;专科招生专业（（见学校招生网站（招生网 (jxuspt.com)）、官方公众号（江西软件职业技术大学招就处）公示信息，各省招生专业具体按照各省计划专刊公布专业执行）</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第六章&nbsp; 录取原则</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十七条&nbsp;&nbsp;我校实行“学校负责、省（市、区）招办监督”的录取体制，坚持择优录取的原则，考虑考生综合素质，公平、公正、公开、科学、规范地选拔学生。学校招生工作实施“阳光工程”，接受广大考生及其家长和社会各方面的监督。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十八条&nbsp;&nbsp;普通文、理科录取原则：专业志愿优先，依据分数，择优录取。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第十九条&nbsp;&nbsp;艺体类录取原则：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（一）美术类专业，要求无色盲，文理兼收。我校不单独设立校考，采用各省（市、自治区）艺术类联考成绩，执行各省综合分计算规则，遵循专业志愿优先，依据综合分排名，择优录取。如遇综合分相同，按高考文化成绩从高到低择优录取，如高考文化成绩相同，则按数学、语文、外语、综合成绩依次排序。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（二）体育类专业，采用各省（市、自治区）体育类专业联考成绩，文化成绩过线后，按专业成绩从高到低择优录取，如专业成绩相同，按高考文化成绩排序，如高考文化成绩相同，则按数学、语文、外语、综合成绩依次排序。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十条&nbsp;&nbsp;学校对各省（市、自治区）的优惠加分政策均按国家教育部及有关省份高考加分、降分政策执行，在录取时予以认可。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十一条&nbsp;&nbsp;均承认各省（自治区、直辖市）对于特殊考生的加分或降分政策，按照考生所报志愿从高分到低分依次择优录取。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十二条&nbsp;&nbsp;按照顺序志愿投档的批次，我校原则上在公布招生计划的120%以内，确定调阅考生档案的比例；按照平行志愿投档的批次，调档比例原则上控制在105%以内；各省级招办有规定的按照规定执行。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十三条&nbsp;&nbsp;考生在参加高等学校招生考试过程中有严重不诚信行为或高考电子档案中有不诚信记录的，我校可不予录取。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十四条&nbsp;&nbsp;对考生身体健康状况要求，我校按照教育部、卫生部、中国残疾人联合会颁发的《普通高等学校招生体检工作指导意见》（教学字2003[3]号）及相关省（市、区）规定执行，考生应根据《普通高等学校招生体检标准》的有关规定，选报符合自己身体条件的专业，否则，学校有权调剂到其它适合的专业，如不服从调剂，则作退档处理。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十五条&nbsp;&nbsp;鉴于教育部、各省正在进行各类招生制度改革，我校以上录取原则若与教育部、各省录取原则有冲突，以教育部、各省公布的录取政策为准。</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89); caret-color: red;">第七章&nbsp; 新生入学及资格复查</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89); caret-color: red;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十六条&nbsp;&nbsp;按国家招生规定录取的新生，持录取通知书，按学校有关要求和规定的期限到校办理入学手续。因故不能按期入学的，应当向学校请假。未请假或者请假逾期的，除因不可抗力等正当事由以外，视为放弃入学资格。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十七条&nbsp;&nbsp;新生入学后，学校将在三个月内进行入学资格复查。复查不合格者，学校将根据国家有关规定视情况予以处理，直至取消入学资格。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十八条&nbsp;&nbsp;凡发现有弄虚作假者，一经查实，取消其入学资格或学籍。</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89); caret-color: red;">第八章&nbsp; 入学学籍及毕（结））业证书种类</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二十九条&nbsp;&nbsp;凡经生源所在地省级高招部门办理正式录取手续的考生，按时来校报到后，在我省教育厅办理学籍注册，取得普通高等教育学籍；学生在学校规定学习年限内，修完教育教学计划规定内容，成绩合格，达到学校毕业要求的，颁发江西软件职业技术大学普通高等教育本（专）科毕业证书。符合学位授予条件的，颁发学位证书。</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89); caret-color: red;">第九章&nbsp; 收费标准、奖贷学金及退学退费办法</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十条&nbsp; 学费：&nbsp;按照省发展改革委、省财政厅、省教育厅核定的收费标准及有关规定收费。具体收费标准以学校官网公示为准。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十一条&nbsp;&nbsp;资助政策：学校建立起了国家奖学金、国家励志奖学金、国家助学金、国家助学贷款、服兵役国家教育资助、勤工助学、学费减免等多种形式有机结合的高校家庭经济困难学生资助政策体系。家庭经济困难学生入校后，学校对其家庭经济困难情况进行核实，采取不同措施给予资助。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十二条&nbsp;&nbsp;退学退费办法：如学生有特殊原因要求退学，我校按照江西省教育厅《江西省民办高校退学退费办法》的规定，办理退学退费手续。</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89); caret-color: red;">第十章&nbsp; 附则</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十三条&nbsp;&nbsp;本章程若与国家法律、法规、章程、规范和上级有关政策不符，按国家法律、法规、章程、规范和上级有关政策执行。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十四条&nbsp;&nbsp;我校不委托任何中介机构或个人进行高考招生录取工作，请考生和家长不要上当受骗。对以学校名义进行非法招生宣传和招生录取等活动的中介机构或个人，学校保留依法追究其责任的权利。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十五条&nbsp;&nbsp;本章程未尽事宜，由我校与各省（市、区）高考招生职能部门协商解决。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十六条&nbsp;本章程自公布之日起生效，由我校招生办公室负责解释。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十七条&nbsp;学校法定代表人、办学许可证查询网站：www.jxedu.gov.cn。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三十八条&nbsp;&nbsp;联系方式：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">招生咨询电话：0791-83792888（传真）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">学校网址：http://www.jxuspt.com</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">监督电话：0791－83792364</p><p><br/></p>